  "prompt": "Which hashtag will I use to get more likes in Instagram?",
  "response": "Using the right hashtags on Instagram can significantly boost your visibility and increase your chances of getting more likes. Here are some tips and popular hashtags you can use:\n\n---\n\n### **Tips for Choosing Hashtags:**\n1. **Be Specific**: Use hashtags that are relevant to your content and niche.\n2. **Mix Popular and Niche Hashtags**: Combine highly popular hashtags with less competitive ones to reach a broader audience.\n3. **Use Trending Hashtags**: Keep an eye on trending topics and hashtags in your industry.\n4. **Create Branded Hashtags**: Encourage followers to use your unique hashtag.\n5. **Avoid Overused Hashtags**: Extremely generic hashtags (e.g., #love, #instagood) may not help you stand out.\n\n---\n\n### **Popular Instagram Hashtags by Category:**\n\n#### **General Engagement:**\n- #instagood\n- #photooftheday\n- #picoftheday\n- #instagram\n- #instadaily\n- #likeforlikes\n- #followme\n- #followforfollowback\n\n#### **Travel:**\n- #travelgram\n- #wanderlust\n- #travelphotography\n- #naturelovers\n- #exploremore\n- #adventuretime\n\n#### **Food:**\n- #foodporn\n- #foodie\n- #yum\n- #instafood\n- #foodphotography\n- #delicious\n\n#### **Fitness & Wellness:**\n- #fitspo\n- #gymlife\n- #workoutmotivation\n- #healthylifestyle\n- #yogalife\n- #fitnessgoals\n\n#### **Fashion:**\n- #ootd\n- #fashionista\n- #styleinspo\n- #streetstyle\n- #fashionblogger\n- #lookbook\n\n#### **Photography:**\n- #photography\n- #portraitphotography\n- #naturephotography\n- #landscapephotography\n- #lensculture\n- #instaphoto\n\n#### **Art & Creativity:**\n- #artistsoninstagram\n- #creativeprocess\n- #digitalart\n- #handmade\n- #artlovers\n- #inspiration\n\n#### **Pets & Animals:**\n- #petsofinstagram\n- #dogsofinstagram\n- #catsofinstagram\n- #animallovers\n- #cuteanimals\n\n#### **Lifestyle:**\n- #lifestyleblogger\n- #selfcare\n- #mindfulness\n- #dailyvibe\n- #homedecor\n- #slowliving\n\n---\n\n### **Tools to Find Hashtags:**\n- **Hashtagify**: Helps discover trending hashtags.\n- **All Hashtag**: Generates hashtag suggestions.\n- **Instagram Search**: Type a keyword in Instagram\u2019s search bar to see related hashtags.\n\n---\n\n### **Pro Tip:**\nUse up to 30 hashtags per post, but aim for a mix of popularity and relevance. Avoid using the same set of hashtags repeatedly, as Instagram may flag this as spammy behavior. \n\nBy consistently using the right hashtags and engaging with your audience, you\u2019ll see an increase in likes and followers! \ud83d\udc4d",
  "temperature": 1.0,
